PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (FORT SELKIRK HISTORIC SITE, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of a number of tracts of land in the Yukon Territory, until August 31, 2005, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1997-1425.
